Exe3

We start by reading and visualizing the data:

In red we can see units associated to handmade tattoo, in black to machine. We can see that price seems correlated with dimension, and ncolors. We start by fitting the linear model:

tatu$method = factor(tatu$method)
m0 = lm(price ~ .*method, data = tatu)
summary(m0)
